beer.beer_description: Surf Rider is our release for the annual WCIPA challenge at The Malthouse. Inspired by 60's surf rock hailing from southern California while also channeling our inner movie buff with a nod to pulp fiction soundtrack. Close your eyes and imagine the sea breeze on your face, crashing waves of guitar driven salty surf rock while you sip on this classic WCIPA. Brewed with Columbus, Amarillo, Citra and Idaho 7 hops.
